{"tid":1454767,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【 追究811 | 民意戰】一人一信聲討衛生署要求解釋催淚煙影響！","createTime":"2019-08-12T08:17:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:40:28.000Z","uid":82203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55f8c711167d63332dcfeb8ed1cd5b3a9262a53c","tid":1454767,"uid":82203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:17:54.000Z","msg":"利申: 小弟係位80後嘅示威者<br />\n<br />\n鑑於嘅狗完全喪失理智<br />\n唔理民居、地鐵站、老少幼童狂放過期山埃彈放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係職場發現，好多中產、家長、成年人其實好care啲煙對健康嘅影響<br />\n而佢地有一部份其實係政治冷感/中立<br />\n<br />\n如果我地瘋狂去信衛生署，我地可以: <br />\n1. 逼使佢地作岀回應,衞生署作為政府的衞生事務顧問, 必須回應<br />\n2. 為民發聲，增加佢地對示威者嘅好感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 拉攏民意，增加支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟寫咗封信，文筆不好，還望指正<br />\n第3項大家可以自由改地鐵站，太古葵芳都得<br />\n同埋我只係以啲居民嘅身份去寫<br />\n各位可以自由加一堆問題要求回應<br />\nSend 去 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">send to enquiries@dh.gov.hk<br />\nsend to enquiries@dh.gov.hk<br />\nsend to enquiries@dh.gov.hk<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n衞生處處長陳漢儀醫生:<br />\n<br />\n有關近日警方於不同的民居，甚至地鐵站內發出大量催淚煙/氣體，本人有以下的查詢：<br />\n<br />\n1. 催淚煙/氣體對人體有什麼短期及長期的害處？最近有民間團體的醫生代表簡述一些害處，例如皮膚過敏、腹瀉、影響中樞神經、增加死亡風險等，可否多加解釋並確認該資料正確與否?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%BA%E8%91%86%E8%B3%A2%E7%AD%89%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%B8%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E6%B0%A3%E5%BE%8C%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80-%E9%80%BE-95-%E7%8F%BE%E4%B9%85%E5%92%B3-%E5%92%B3%E8%A1%80%E7%AD%89%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80-728-%E6%AF%94-612-%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D/?fbclid=IwAR3BxvX3lH6-_nTLWqziYk-fCqckH3a-x2n1UzKrpZtHCWC1zDzlu1TmfgA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25BA%25E8%2591%2586%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580-%25E9%2580%25BE-95-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%2592%25B3-%25E5%2592%25B3%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2591%25BC%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580-728-%25E6%25AF%2594-612-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BxvX3lH6-_nTLWqziYk-fCqckH3a-x2n1UzKrpZtHCWC1zDzlu1TmfgA&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ0igq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=871640b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2584%25BA%25E8%2591%2586%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25A0%2594%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%2590%25B8%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580-%25E9%2580%25BE-95-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E4%25B9%2585%25E5%2592%25B3-%25E5%2592%25B3%25E8%25A1%2580%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2591%25BC%25E5%2590%25B8%25E7%25B3%25BB%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E7%2597%2587%25E7%258B%2580-728-%25E6%25AF%2594-612-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BxvX3lH6-_nTLWqziYk-fCqckH3a-x2n1UzKrpZtHCWC1zDzlu1TmfgA&h=8126eb32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%84%BA%E8%91%86%E8%B3%A2%E7%AD%89%E7%A0%94%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E5%90%B8%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E6%B0%A3%E5%BE%8C%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80-%E9%80%BE-95-%E7%8F%BE%E4%B9%85%E5%92%B3-%E5%92%B3%E8%A1%80%E7%AD%89%E5%91%BC%E5%90%B8%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E7%97%87%E7%8B%80-728-%E6%AF%94-612-%E6%B8%85%E5%A0%B4%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D/?fbclid=IwAR3BxvX3lH6-_nTLWqziYk-fCqckH3a-x2n1UzKrpZtHCWC1zDzlu1TmfgA</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474057-20190811.htm?fbclid=IwAR1xTQYzTC5m28t7A8Tf0lP9A58hzJ6TuGlWseGjfCBHtl4yu9E_wJ2TZIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474057-20190811.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xTQYzTC5m28t7A8Tf0lP9A58hzJ6TuGlWseGjfCBHtl4yu9E_wJ2TZIc&d=dhMoNY2Sjv1OWPDolMMhQ0igq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=4e176ed1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1474057-20190811.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xTQYzTC5m28t7A8Tf0lP9A58hzJ6TuGlWseGjfCBHtl4yu9E_wJ2TZIc&h=96082e72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1474057-20190811.htm?fbclid=IwAR1xTQYzTC5m28t7A8Tf0lP9A58hzJ6TuGlWseGjfCBHtl4yu9E_wJ2TZIc</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 據媒體報導，催淚煙/氣體的殘餘物會依附在抽風管道。作為普通市民，並經常出入太古城地鐵站，應如何保護自己呢？<br />\n<br />\n3. 小兒現兩個月大，並進食全母乳。作為母親的我，如上所述，經常出入太古城地鐵站，請問吸入催淚煙/氣體後仍可繼續餵哺母乳嗎？<br />\n<br />\n4. 另外，有媒體報導警方所發放的催淚煙為過了期限的，亦傳出可能釋出山埃毒。如果在室內施放這些催淚煙，會對市民構成什麼影響？<br />\n<br />\n衞生署作為政府的衞生事務顧問，期盼上述問題得到你們專業的回覆，以保障香港市民的健康。<br />\n謝謝！<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n光服香港，時代革命<br />\n天滅中共，黑警死全家<br />\n祝各位武運亨通</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5df0c38e538b64289548db12832539ef7d16fc5","tid":1454767,"uid":82203,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbBDE9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbBDE9k.jpg&h=03648f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21c6929c93c513089d5230ec0d6279a81800510","tid":1454767,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"向政府投訴政府"},{"pid":"69d750239bdcd6a7f0d120e55c0a69f9012938fa","tid":1454767,"uid":82203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":